originalText.text:
Byteflow Dynamics is a very fast growing AI consultancy led by Dr. Andi Shehu. It is located in the heart of midtown NYC. I was very fortunate to start my Data Science career under Andi's supervision. He is a very sharp and critical thinker.

His (and his team's) opinions and feedback will not only be immensely helpful, but really essential for the exploration, ideation, and implementation phases of your data science/AI projects.

A lot of businesses still struggle today in identifying the avenues for the successful application of advanced analytics within their firms. Andi's team of enthusiastic data scientists will help you identify those key gaps  and opportunities for enhancing your business by identifying the avenues for the applications of advanced statistical/AI techniques.
